    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Washington D.C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "This is not an April Fool joke.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Saturday, April 1, 1950 at about 6 P.M. I was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "driving north on Route 47 - west of Geneva, Illinois",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "and a little north of St. Charles, Illinois. Just",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "ahead, thru the windshield I saw a silvery white",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "object in the sky. It was traveling west at about",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the speed of an airplane. It was shaped like",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "this [drawing of a trapezoid]. I was driving at 35 M.P.H. and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "slowed down to 20 M.P.H. to watch this object.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "It went behind a white cloud and I continued",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "to watch but the object did not come out from",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "behind the cloud as far as I could see.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Geneva is 35 miles west of Chicago, and just",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "north of Chicago is the Glenview Airport, operated I",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "believe by the Navy. The Saturday Evening",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Post carried an article sometime ago about the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Flying Saucers and it said to report anything",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "like the above to the F.B.I.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
